{"word":"εἰλυφάζω","slug":"εἰλυφάζω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>εἰλυφάζω</b></el> <el>(εἰλῡφάζω,) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b>= <a href='S:εἰλύω'><el>εἰλύω</el></a>\n<br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b>only in <a href='S:present tense'>pres.</a> and <a href='S:imperfect tense'>imperf.</a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>to roll along</i> (<a href='S:transitive'>trans.</a>), <b><a href='S:Iliad'>Il.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><a href='S:intransitive'>intr.</a> <i>to roll</i> or <i>whirl about</i>, of a torch, <b><a href='S:Hesiod'>Hes.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}